@annarev, @hsgkim actually it is a naming conflict as tf.extract_volume_patches is not loaded in version 1.12. Unfortunately the new op is not mentioned in the release notes (I checked before upgrading).

The implementation in 1.12 is nearly the same as mine. Nevertheless I also implemented the gradient for the op (integrate_volume_patches). If there is interest in the implementation I can share.

Thanks for the support.
